PN,30301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,FAs many as half of convenience stores
OL,7,Fand vape retailers in some areas are
OL,8,Festimated to have links with organised
OL,9,Fcrime, according to a Trading
OL,10,FStandards report.
OL,12,FSimilarly, up to a third of American
OL,13,Fcandy stores and one in four fast food
OL,14,Ftakeaways in specific areas are
OL,15,Fsuspected of being a front for
OL,16,Fcriminal activity, the organisation's
OL,17,FHidden In Plain Sight report said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,FA survey by Trading Standards found
OL,7,Fthat 97% of its officers are aware of
OL,8,Fsuspected organised crime groups
OL,9,F(OCGs) operating out of retail
OL,10,Fpremises on their local high streets.
OL,12,FThere was also "almost universal
OL,13,Frecognition" ` involving 99% of
OL,14,Fofficers ` that Trading Standards had
OL,15,Fseen an increase in the number of cash-
OL,16,Fintensive businesses opening on their
OL,17,Flocal high streets since 2020.
OL,26,@tD@POUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,FAlmost three quarters of Trading
OL,7,FStandards professionals (72%) reported
OL,8,Fexperiencing intimidatory behaviour or
OL,9,Fhad been threatened with violence in
OL,10,Fthe course of their duties.
OL,12,FTrading Standards has published a map
OL,13,Fof high streets across the UK for so-
OL,14,Fcalled dodgy shops, along with the 10
OL,15,Ftowns and cities perceived by its
OL,16,Fofficers to be hot spots for OCGs,
OL,17,Fwith Birmingham, Liverpool and London
OL,18,Ffilling the top three spots.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,FIt said the budgets of Local Authority
OL,7,FTrading Standards (LATS) services had
OL,8,Fbeen cut by up to 50% over the last
OL,9,Fdecade, with staffing stripped to
OL,10,Fminimum levels.
OL,12,FTrading Standards warned that this `
OL,13,Fcoupled with resource "challenges" for
OL,14,Fother key enforcement agencies
OL,15,Fincluding police ` had coincided with
OL,16,Fthe rapid spread of dodgy shops across
OL,17,Fthe UK, as well as complex criminal
OL,18,Fnetworks that underpinned them.
OL,26,@uD@WOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,FDodgy shops had a "profound impact" on
OL,7,Fthe safety of the public and the
OL,8,Fviability of the legitimate businesses
OL,9,Faround them, while putting the health
OL,10,Fof consumers, including children, at
OL,11,Frisk.
OL,13,FThese shops often brought with them
OL,14,Fassociated criminality including anti-
OL,15,Fsocial behaviour, theft and violent
OL,16,Fcrime, drug supply, modern slavery,
OL,17,Fand child sexual exploitation.
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,FThe report outlined a 10-point plan to
OL,7,F"reclaim the UK's high streets",
OL,8,Fincluding investing in Trading
OL,9,FStandards, making the sale of illegal
OL,10,Fgoods a trigger for licence review,
OL,11,Fand an additional #20 million to
OL,12,Fbolster Trading Standards resources
OL,13,Ffor ports and borders.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,FJohn Herriman, chief executive of the
OL,7,FChartered Trading Standards Institute
OL,8,F(CTSI), said: "It is clear from this
OL,9,Fresearch that serious and organised
OL,10,Fcrime is endemic across the UK, and
OL,11,Fthe threat posed by illegitimate high
OL,12,Fstreet businesses is having a
OL,13,Fsignificant impact on the work of
OL,14,FTrading Standards, and our ability to
OL,15,Fprotect consumers and maintain the
OL,16,Flevel playing field for legitimate
OL,17,Fbusiness.
OL,26,@pD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,F"Local Authority Trading Standards
OL,7,Fservices have faced damaging funding
OL,8,Fcuts of up to 50% over the past
OL,9,Fdecade, with key enforcement partners
OL,10,Fexperiencing similar resourcing
OL,11,Fchallenges.
OL,13,F"We recognise that the Government is
OL,14,Ffocussed on this issue, but it must
OL,15,Furgently bring together and properly
OL,16,Finvest in enforcement agencies `
OL,17,Fincluding Local Authority Trading
OL,18,FStandards ` to give us the powers and
OL,19,Fresources needed to tackle what is a
OL,20,Fwidespread and growing national
OL,21,Fproblem."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,FAssociation of Convenience Stores
OL,7,Fchief executive, Ed Woodall, said:
OL,8,F"Responsible convenience retailers are
OL,9,Fextremely frustrated with rogue
OL,10,Ftraders operating with impunity in
OL,11,Ftheir local area.
OL,13,F"85% of retailers asked in our 2026
OL,14,FCrime Survey said that illicit trading
OL,15,Fhas increased in their local area `
OL,16,Fthis cannot be allowed to continue.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,F"We have consistently called for
OL,7,FTrading Standards to be given the
OL,8,Fresources they need to tackle the
OL,9,Fdangerous and growing illicit market
OL,10,Fblighting communities across the UK.
OL,12,F"Tens of millions of pounds need to be
OL,13,Finvested in local enforcement capacity
OL,14,Fto shut down these rogue traders and
OL,15,Fsupport the responsible retailers that
OL,16,Fare suffering as a result."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,FThe Independent British Vape Trade
OL,7,FAssociation chief executive Gillian
OL,8,FGolden said: "We commend CTSI and the
OL,9,FACG for putting together this report
OL,10,Fand fully endorse their 10-point plan.
OL,12,F"The media often conflate organised
OL,13,Fcriminal networks with law-abiding
OL,14,Fvape businesses, when in fact these
OL,15,Fcriminals just see illicit vapes as a
OL,16,Fcommodity in the same way as illicit
OL,17,Ftobacco or counterfeit goods. That has
OL,18,Fdamaged the public's understanding of
OL,19,Four sector.
OL,26,@pD@NOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777514612
OL,3,CHalf of convenience and vape stores in
OL,4,Csome areas linked to organised crime
OL,6,F"We have already seen where greater
OL,7,Finter-agency working to tackle
OL,8,Forganised crime has been successful.
OL,9,FIt would be an even greater win for
OL,10,Flegitimatise businesses and consumers
OL,11,Fif the Government takes forward these
OL,12,Frecommendations."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@QO]
